{"image_id": "AKAM_2010_page_87", "image_size": [1257, 1632], "ocr": [{"text": "provide Akamai services to acerno customers; a trained technical workforce in place in the United States; an", "bbox": [153.2, 149.8, 1103.8, 170.6]}, {"text": "existing sales pipeline and a trained sales force. In accordance with current accounting standards, goodwill", "bbox": [153.2, 174.8, 1103.7, 195.7]}, {"text": "associated with the acerno acquisition will not be amortized and will be tested for impairment at least annually", "bbox": [153.2, 199.8, 1103.7, 220.7]}, {"text": "(see Note 9).", "bbox": [153.2, 224.8, 260.4, 245.7]}, {"text": "The following table presents the allocation of the purchase price for acerno:", "bbox": [194.9, 269.4, 827.6, 290.3]}, {"text": "(In thousands)", "bbox": [917.2, 308.7, 1020.5, 325.4]}, {"text": "Total consideration:", "bbox": [236.6, 339.0, 404.0, 359.9]}, {"text": "Cash paid . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [278.3, 364.1, 885.9, 384.9]}, {"text": "$89,520", "bbox": [934.9, 364.1, 1002.7, 384.9]}, {"text": "Transaction costs . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [278.3, 389.1, 885.9, 409.9]}, {"text": "1,294", "bbox": [955.8, 389.1, 1002.7, 409.9]}, {"text": "Total purchase consideration . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [320.0, 422.4, 885.9, 443.3]}, {"text": "$90,814", "bbox": [934.9, 422.4, 1002.7, 443.3]}, {"text": "Allocation of the purchase consideration:", "bbox": [236.6, 459.9, 580.9, 480.8]}, {"text": "Current assets . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [278.3, 484.9, 885.9, 505.8]}, {"text": "$ 5,249", "bbox": [934.9, 484.9, 1002.7, 505.8]}, {"text": "Property and equipment . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [278.3, 510.0, 885.9, 530.8]}, {"text": "1,720", "bbox": [955.8, 510.0, 1002.7, 530.8]}, {"text": "Identifiable intangible assets . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [278.3, 535.0, 885.9, 555.8]}, {"text": "19,400", "bbox": [945.4, 535.0, 1002.7, 555.8]}, {"text": "Goodwill . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [278.3, 560.0, 885.9, 580.8]}, {"text": "80,901", "bbox": [945.4, 560.0, 1002.7, 580.8]}, {"text": "Deferred tax liabilities . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [278.3, 585.0, 885.9, 605.8]}, {"text": "(7,516)", "bbox": [948.8, 585.0, 1009.6, 605.8]}, {"text": "Other liabilities assumed . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [278.3, 610.0, 885.9, 630.9]}, {"text": "(8,940)", "bbox": [948.8, 610.0, 1009.6, 630.9]}, {"text": "$90,814", "bbox": [934.9, 643.4, 1002.7, 664.2]}, {"text": "The following were the identified intangible assets acquired and the respective estimated periods over which", "bbox": [194.9, 700.5, 1103.8, 721.3]}, {"text": "such assets will be amortized:", "bbox": [153.2, 725.5, 402.5, 746.3]}, {"text": "Amount", "bbox": [877.1, 798.1, 935.5, 814.8]}, {"text": "Weighted", "bbox": [991.3, 764.8, 1059.9, 781.4]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [995.9, 781.4, 1055.2, 798.1]}, {"text": "useful life", "bbox": [991.2, 798.1, 1060.1, 814.8]}, {"text": "(In thousands)", "bbox": [854.7, 823.1, 958.0, 839.8]}, {"text": "(In years)", "bbox": [991.1, 823.1, 1060.1, 839.8]}, {"text": "Completed technologies . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [194.9, 845.1, 823.4, 866.0]}, {"text": "$ 9,200", "bbox": [872.4, 845.1, 940.1, 866.0]}, {"text": "2.5", "bbox": [1012.6, 845.1, 1038.6, 866.0]}, {"text": "Customer relationships . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [194.9, 870.1, 823.4, 891.0]}, {"text": "4,300", "bbox": [893.2, 870.1, 940.1, 891.0]}, {"text": "4.1", "bbox": [1012.6, 870.1, 1038.6, 891.0]}, {"text": "Non-compete agreements . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [194.9, 895.1, 823.4, 916.0]}, {"text": "5,600", "bbox": [893.2, 895.1, 940.1, 916.0]}, {"text": "2.5", "bbox": [1012.6, 895.1, 1038.6, 916.0]}, {"text": "Trade names . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [194.9, 920.1, 823.4, 941.0]}, {"text": "300", "bbox": [908.9, 920.1, 940.1, 941.0]}, {"text": "1.5", "bbox": [1012.6, 920.1, 1038.6, 941.0]}, {"text": "Total . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [194.9, 953.5, 823.4, 974.3]}, {"text": "$19,400", "bbox": [872.4, 953.5, 940.1, 974.3]}, {"text": "In determining the purchase price allocation, the Company considered, among other factors, its intention to", "bbox": [194.9, 1010.6, 1103.8, 1031.5]}, {"text": "use the acquired assets and the historical and estimated future demand for acerno services. The fair value of", "bbox": [153.2, 1035.6, 1103.7, 1056.5]}, {"text": "intangible assets was based upon the income approach. In applying this approach, the values of the intangible", "bbox": [153.2, 1060.6, 1103.6, 1081.5]}, {"text": "assets acquired were determined using projections of revenues and expenses specifically attributed to the", "bbox": [153.2, 1085.6, 1103.7, 1106.5]}, {"text": "intangible assets. The income streams were then discounted to present value using estimated risk-adjusted", "bbox": [153.2, 1110.7, 1103.5, 1131.5]}, {"text": "discount rates. The rate used to discount the expected future net cash flows from the intangible assets to their", "bbox": [153.2, 1135.7, 1103.6, 1156.5]}, {"text": "present values was based upon a weighted average cost of capital of 15%. The discount rate was determined after", "bbox": [153.2, 1160.7, 1103.6, 1181.5]}, {"text": "consideration of market rates of return on debt and equity capital, the weighted average return on invested capital", "bbox": [153.2, 1185.7, 1103.6, 1206.5]}, {"text": "and the risk associated with achieving forecasted sales related to the technology and assets acquired from acerno.", "bbox": [153.2, 1210.7, 1098.1, 1231.5]}, {"text": "The customer relationships were valued using the excess earnings method of income approach. The key", "bbox": [194.9, 1255.3, 1103.8, 1276.1]}, {"text": "assumptions used in valuing the customer relationships were as follows: discount rate of 15%, tax rate of 35%", "bbox": [153.2, 1280.3, 1103.7, 1301.2]}, {"text": "and estimated average economic life of seven years.", "bbox": [153.2, 1305.3, 588.2, 1326.2]}, {"text": "The relief-from-royalty method was used to value the completed technologies acquired from acerno. The", "bbox": [194.9, 1349.9, 1103.8, 1370.8]}, {"text": "relief-from-royalty method estimates the cost savings that accrue to the owner of an intangible asset that would", "bbox": [153.2, 1374.9, 1103.8, 1395.8]}, {"text": "otherwise be required to pay royalties or license fees on revenues earned through the use of the asset. The royalty", "bbox": [153.2, 1400.0, 1103.6, 1420.8]}, {"text": "rate used is based on an analysis of empirical, market-derived royalty rates for guideline intangible assets.", "bbox": [153.2, 1425.0, 1103.6, 1445.8]}, {"text": "65", "bbox": [618.1, 1475.4, 638.9, 1496.2]}]}